Privacy Policy - Study Sensei

PRIVACY POLICY
Last updated: October 15, 2025

This Privacy Notice for Study Sensei ("we," "us," or "our") describes how and why we might access, collect, store, use, and/or share ("process") your personal information when you use our services ("Services"), including when you:

- Download and use our mobile application (Study Sensei) or any other linked application.
- Engage with us in other related ways, including sales, marketing, or events.

Questions or concerns? Reading this Privacy Notice will help you understand your privacy rights and choices. If you do not agree with our policies, please do not use our Services. For questions, contact us at m.saridae@gmail.com.

---------------------------------
SUMMARY OF KEY POINTS
---------------------------------
- We collect personal information that you provide, such as name, email, password, and age.
- We do not collect sensitive personal information or data from third parties.
- Your data is processed to deliver, improve, and administer our services securely.
- We share data only when required, such as in business transfers.
- We use AI-based tools (like Google Cloud AI) responsibly and securely.
- Your personal data is retained only as long as needed for our services.
- We maintain security measures, but no system is 100% secure.
- You may review, change, or terminate your account anytime.

